{"tid":702352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南華早報：中國批准高通收購 NXP","createTime":"2018-06-14T23:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T03:48:23.000Z","uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"429e1e9a3a4ec4e62d51337d0c7f15904e70fb7b","tid":702352,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:28:19.000Z","msg":"南華早報引述知情人士報導，中國監管機構已批准高通（Qualcomm）收購恩智浦半導體（NXP Semiconductors）的計畫。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，恩智浦盤後大漲10.7%；高通漲 3%。"},{"pid":"b211a3cb7b05e05eb6439bbe78c2889edf52e9a6","tid":702352,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:29:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.scmp.com/business/companies/article/2150894/chinese-regulators-approve-qualcomm-purchase-nxp-us44-billion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Farticle%2F2150894%2Fchinese-regulators-approve-qualcomm-purchase-nxp-us44-billion&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f2972850\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.scmp.com/business/companies/article/2150894/chinese-regulators-approve-qualcomm-purchase-nxp-us44-billion</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Chinese regulators approve Qualcomm purchase of NXP for US$44 billion, sources say</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nThe ruling clears an antitrust roadblock caused by trade tensions between the US and Beijing<br />\n<br />\nPUBLISHED : Friday, 15 June, 2018, 6:07am<br />\nUPDATED : Friday, 15 June, 2018, 6:41am<br />\n<br />\nChinese regulators have approved US semiconductor company Qualcomm&rsquo;s proposed US$44 billion acquisition of Dutch chip maker NXP Semiconductors, according to people with knowledge of the matter."},{"pid":"d14abec84dc40ea9916288cadaa17c2201061393","tid":702352,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"The decision by China&rsquo;s Ministry of Commerce, or &ldquo;Mofcom&rdquo;, clears a months-long antitrust roadblock caused by trade tensions between the US and Beijing and will allow the takeover to proceed.<br />\n<br />\nAntitrust regulators from nine nations had been required to sign off on the merger because of its potential impact on their economies, and after eight others &ndash; including the US and Japan &ndash; had approved the deal, it awaited China&rsquo;s decision."},{"pid":"876a1f318134479963c58a5244b7d658bc078ada","tid":702352,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf78b8e19c24438267bd5be9e0247cc77ca2031a","tid":702352,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5fb75b1909bb7edb216fc47d574a1c8a73baba","tid":702352,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:24:41.000Z","msg":"啲人又話唔批NXP係貿易戰談判籌碼<br />\n而家贏国一路減減減稅，又批准埋收購<br />\n<br />\n睇黎贏国贏太多，想讓多幾球先亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a757b092d317c734648eda378a7885eabcf4afb","tid":702352,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"其實關中國咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd83dea2ddb2f1790b07d3e673f829e0fe3c8d2","tid":702352,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"J還J<br />\n<br />\n我估係戰略佈署<br />\n<br />\n反CUP 高通D技術"},{"pid":"045eebd5fd57726d2b1e2749d5b63bf59f587fec","tid":702352,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a757b092d317c734648eda378a7885eabcf4afb","tid":702352,"uid":693,"like":0,"disli